[{"index":1,"title":"曾经的天使","content":"&nbsp;&nbsp;我叫雨曦，今年14岁，在悦阳中学读初二。&nbsp;\r<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;在这个班上，同学们都叫我“怪胎”。一是因为我的性格非常冷血，不爱说话，惹我的人下场都会很惨。二是我从来不会哭，无论遇到什么事，我都不会哭。&nbsp;\r<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;可是他一来，什么，好像都改变了。他叫天林，是插班生。我觉得他很讨厌，整天嬉皮笑脸的，让我看了就恶心。还有，也不知道这个糊涂老师怎么安排的，竟然让他坐在我前面。最可气的是，一到夏天，天气那么热，天林就把窗帘拉开晒太阳，有时候我再把窗帘拉上，他就扯着嗓门对我说：“大小姐，晒太阳多舒服啊，你应该多晒晒！”说完，又把窗帘拉开。&nbsp;\r<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;虽然我气不打一处来，但想想也觉得可笑，他那么喜欢晒太阳，嗯，应该到沙漠里去。&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>&nbsp;\r<br>&nbsp;\r<br>\u0018","author":"咖啡欧白烟","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.d517a4b7.xxh8aLECIY2TvruzKbsiqA&fr=pb","date":"2008-07-01 19:01","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":2,"title":"回复：曾经的天使","content":"冒昧的说一下。。。。。\r<br>\r<br>\r<br>发帖格式换下","author":"asd425798","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.7ba934e.OrAClIFR_SZhZeaiJAqbiQ&fr=pb","date":"2008-07-01 19:04","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":3,"title":"回复：曾经的天使","content":"贴的题目要加个\n\n【原创�","author":"asd425798","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.7ba934e.OrAClIFR_SZhZeaiJAqbiQ&fr=pb","date":"2008-07-01 19:04","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":4,"title":"回复：曾经的天使","content":"本来我也想说的……\n不过觉得太唐突了……\n所以就讪讪的走了…�","author":"孤独∫少年","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.ed719bdb.Mutw1NkFuoah5aC7dY_M2g&fr=pb","date":"2008-07-01 19:05","ip":null,"old_image":"http://hiphotos.baidu.com/yumendouzhanyongle/pic/item/73c914f5609c3936bd310932.jpg","user_sign_image":null},{"index":5,"title":"回复：曾经的天使","content":"有病么�","author":"蓝颜郁落云","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.50fe07f.NZWhaNdDo_byP9UCSxI6Dw&fr=pb","date":"2008-07-01 21:20","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":6,"title":"回复：曾经的天使","content":"...似乎需要重发...谢谢...","author":"酷睿少年","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.f4a2d792.gLGjYSqX9ncYWgITk-avaA&fr=pb","date":"2008-07-02 14:42","ip":null,"old_image":null,"us